Thinkpad T495 is an AMD-based laptop series.

== Troubleshooting ==

=== Display brightness can't be controlled ===

The [[AMDGPU]] driver requires the vanilla-sources [[kernel]] in order to load correctly. Otherwise you will not be able to change the brightness of the display.

